---
import gameplay1_3 from '../assets/images/gameplay1_3.png';
---

<section id="tips" class="game-tips section">
  <div class="tips-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-badge">Pro Tips</div>
      <h2>Become a Cheese Champion</h2>
      <p>Master these expert strategies and dominate the arena in Cheese Chompers 3D! From timing your jumps to using momentum, these tips will help you become the last rat standing.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tips-content">
      <div class="tips-image">
        <div class="image-frame">
          <div class="image-glow"></div>
          <img src={gameplay1_3.src} alt="Cheese Chompers 3D Strategy" width="500" height="300" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="image-overlay"></div>
          <div class="image-badge">
            <span>Pro Strategies</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tips-list">
        <div class="tip" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <h3>Strategic Timing</h3>
            <p>Time your jumps carefully to avoid being vulnerable when landing. Wait for opponents to jump first, then strike when they're about to land.</p>
            <div class="tip-difficulty">
              <div class="difficulty-label">Difficulty:</div>
              <div class="difficulty-meter">
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M13.49 5.48c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2s-.9-2-2-2-2 .9-2 2 .9 2 2 2zm-3.6 13.9l1-4.4 2.1 2v6h2v-7.5l-2.1-2 .6-3c1.3 1.5 3.3 2.5 5.5 2.5v-2c-1.9 0-3.5-1-4.3-2.4l-1-1.6c-.4-.6-1-1-1.7-1-.3 0-.5.1-.8.1l-5.2 2.2v4.7h2v-3.4l1.8-.7-1.6 8.1-4.9-1-.4 2 7 1.4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <h3>Speed Boost Mastery</h3>
            <p>Use the mid-air flip for speed boosts when chasing opponents or escaping danger. Chain multiple flips together for extended bursts of speed.</p>
            <div class="tip-difficulty">
              <div class="difficulty-label">Difficulty:</div>
              <div class="difficulty-meter">
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <h3>Group Tactics</h3>
            <p>Position yourself strategically to push multiple opponents at once during chaotic moments. Target rats that are already close to the edge for easier knockouts.</p>
            <div class="tip-difficulty">
              <div class="difficulty-label">Difficulty:</div>
              <div class="difficulty-meter">
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <h3>Center Control</h3>
            <p>Stay near the center of the platform when possible to minimize risk. This gives you more reaction time and escape routes when opponents charge at you.</p>
            <div class="tip-difficulty">
              <div class="difficulty-label">Difficulty:</div>
              <div class="difficulty-meter">
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M15.5 14h-.79l-.28-.27C15.41 12.59 16 11.11 16 9.5 16 5.91 13.09 3 9.5 3S3 5.91 3 9.5 5.91 16 9.5 16c1.61 0 3.09-.59 4.23-1.57l.27.28v.79l5 4.99L20.49 19l-4.99-5zm-6 0C7.01 14 5 11.99 5 9.5S7.01 5 9.5 5 14 7.01 14 9.5 11.99 14 9.5 14z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <h3>Pattern Recognition</h3>
            <p>Observe opponent patterns and target predictable players for easier knockouts. Many players follow consistent movement patterns that you can exploit.</p>
            <div class="tip-difficulty">
              <div class="difficulty-label">Difficulty:</div>
              <div class="difficulty-meter">
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.38 8.57l-1.23 1.85a8 8 0 0 1-.22 7.58H5.07A8 8 0 0 1 15.58 6.85l1.85-1.23A10 10 0 0 0 3.35 19a2 2 0 0 0 1.72 1h13.85a2 2 0 0 0 1.74-1 10 10 0 0 0-.27-10.44z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <h3>Momentum Management</h3>
            <p>Use your rat's weight and movement to deliver more powerful impacts against opponents. Build up speed before colliding with other rats for maximum effect.</p>
            <div class="tip-difficulty">
              <div class="difficulty-label">Difficulty:</div>
              <div class="difficulty-meter">
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="700">
          <div class="tip-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M3 3v18h18V3H3zm16 16H5V5h14v14zM11 7h2v2h-2V7zM7 7h2v2H7V7zm8 0h2v2h-2V7zm-8 4h2v2H7v-2zm4 0h2v2h-2v-2zm4 0h2v2h-2v-2zm-8 4h2v2H7v-2zm4 0h2v2h-2v-2zm4 0h2v2h-2v-2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="tip-content">
            <h3>Edge Tactics</h3>
            <p>Use the arena edges strategically to corner opponents. Position yourself between rivals and the edge to maximize your knockout opportunities. Be careful not to get too close to the edge yourself!</p>
            <div class="tip-difficulty">
              <div class="difficulty-label">Difficulty:</div>
              <div class="difficulty-meter">
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
                <span class="difficulty-level active"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tips-cta">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <div class="cta-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-text">
          <h3>Ready to put these strategies to the test?</h3>
          <p>Jump into the arena and show off your new skills!</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#game" class="btn btn-glow">Play Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .game-tips {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .tips-bg {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 30% 70%, rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.05) 0%, transparent 30%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 30%, rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.05) 0%, transparent 30%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .section-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .tips-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .tips-image {
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-frame {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(5deg);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .image-frame:hover {
    transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(0);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-hover);
  }

  .image-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
    z-index: 1;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .image-frame:hover .image-glow {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .tips-image img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    transition: transform var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .image-frame:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.7), transparent 70%);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .image-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    left: 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    z-index: 3;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
  }

  .tips-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .tip {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(42, 42, 64, 0.7), rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.7));
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
  }

  .tip:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-hover);
    border-color: rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2);
  }

  .tip-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2), rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.1));
    border-radius: 15px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all var(--transition-medium) ease;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 87, 34, 0.2);
  }

  .tip:hover .tip-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1) rotate(10deg);
    box-shadow: var(--neon-glow);
  }

  .tip-content {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .tip-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .tip-content h3::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -5px;
    left: 0;
    width: 30px;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .tip-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .tip-difficulty {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .difficulty-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .difficulty-meter {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .difficulty-level {
    width: 20px;
    height: 6px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .difficulty-level.active {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
  }

  .tips-cta {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-content {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-content::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cg fill='none' fill-rule='evenodd'%3E%3Cg fill='%23FFFFFF' fill-opacity='0.05'%3E%3Cpath d='M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z'/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    opacity: 0.1;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .cta-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--color-white);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  .cta-text {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .cta-text h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .cta-text p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .btn-glow {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .btn-glow:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .tips-content {
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .tips-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .tips-image {
      order: -1;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .image-frame {
      transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(0);
    }

    .cta-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-icon {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
    }

    .cta-text {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .section-header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .tip {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .tip-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .tip {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .tip-icon {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section-badge {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .image-badge {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
